message.body: On 01/26,Monday,Weg's #31,Onondaga is moving walls.R = 11 x 66,A = 4 X 60
Wondering if you can come up to help?
Liz I am so sorry... I have 1 day off this MONTH and no room yo wiggle around any stores. Are you doing it yourself?
Also fingers crossed that the weather holds out!
No, but loosing Chris this week.It's been long time since I moved walls. Lori & Sue never have.
Liz, I'm so sorry that I'm not available to help. Make sure you bring your heavy duty flat screwdriver to pry apart the walls! You will be fine - you can do it!
Thought I would check w/you 1st. It will be ok if you say so!! They will just have to put up w/me....
They are lucky to have you!
